Text:
Come on! Somebody seed this! What's really needed are all the "C" files and the help file. The C files are the 1024x768 sized. A are 640x480 and B are 800x600.

There's many downloads out there with all the C files replaced with dummy files so the game runs but crashes when you try to switch to 1024x768.

A torrent of just the C files and the help file would be much appreciated!

i want this game so bad and i've been looking for it so long... if i manage to finish downloading this torrent, imma seeding this for life... lol

thanx TheDSFSTeam for the release.
